narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Luz Sanchez is a Social Worker provider based in Kissimmee, FL. From 2019-02 through 2023-12, this provider received $384K in Medicaid payments across 5K claims serving 1K beneficiaries, billing 1 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 100% of billing is concentrated in T1017 (T1017), indicating significant specialization in this service.
Spending more than doubled from $34K in 2019 to $171K in 2023 (408% growth).
Saw a 4.5× spike in 2022 ($33K → $147K), a sharp year-over-year increase.
